                <div class="tittle">
                  <h3 class="text-left">About EOS</h3>
                  <p class="text-left"><i>English Online Study is inspired by the many years we have been in the business, coupled with the desire to help and be of help to those who fully seek it. We maintain good and honest transactions among ourselves, with our students and teachers.</i>
                    <hr>
                  </div>
                  <p>The people behind English Online Study saw a lot of potential for a bigger global population to be of helped in reaching out to others in their own web of interest, as well as in areas that they need to connect to, such as their online network through the use of famous social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and Google to name a few; also their need to connect to their working network such as their international partners or their clients from different countries. It is not anymore new to us that many use these platforms as a means of communication, as well as getting as much business as they could and extending their business globally.</p>
                  <p>In light with this far-reaching awareness and an overall view of what is going on in our world today, we have put up a school that will stretch out that kind of service that people need these days for young kids, teenagers, college or university students, travelers, business executives, business owners, parents alike. Our virtual school has a satellite network in Europe, Asia, South and North America that aims to help people from all walks of life to communicate effectively and efficiently using different educational tools that is available online, as well as from our own virtual library, that our students and educators/trainers can use in classes.</p>
                  <p>We aim to give a flexible and fun educational environment, following set standards on a global scale, in educating English as a Second-Language students, facilitating them with professional support from our well-founded and licensed teachers/trainers in studying for IELTS, or TOEFL exams, Business English, and English for Conversation, as well as be a medium of promoting good will to all regardless of race or color, nationality, religion, idealism, status, or class, as ambassador of peace and of universal love.</p>
                  <p>Not only do we aim to educate and help people reach out globally, we are a virtual school that aims to also give more teaching opportunities to educators around the world who are proficient in English Oral Communications skills and are Professionally trained in the field of language education.</p>
                </div>
                <div id="menu1" class="tab-pane fade">
                  <div class="tittle">
                    <h3 class="text-left">Our Team</h3>
                    <p class="text-left"><i>Our mission is to democratize the learning of English in the world providing online education at accessible prices.. </i></p>
                    <hr>
                  </div>
                  <p>Today’s work set-up, be it in school for students or professionals, requires everyone to be mobile and always traveling, which makes internet a crucial part of being able to learn more, or gain more information from and knowledge, regardless of who you are, where you are and what you’re doing.</p>
                  <p>At <b>English Online Study</b>, we definitely give importance to your specific schedules and needs, as well as being accessible anywhere you are anytime you want. This is why it is of utmost importance that we keep a reliable, and dependable database of experienced and professional educators and trainers around the globe to keep up with our students’ demands as regards to class scheduling.
                    <p>We can even have class sessions with you while you’re traveling or taking a vacation outside your country or while you’re taking a break at home, or at your office or even while you’re on a break from your leisure walk at the park, just by using your wireless phone, wifi phone, your tablet or your laptop. It’s that convenient & easy.</p>
                    <p>Our training team consists of highly-skilled English Communicators, holding Bachelor degrees and Masters Degree in their own specialized fields of study, and experienced and effective Online English Educators coming from different English speaking countries from all over the world.</p>
                    <p>We aim to have an extensive database of resources to be able to give more to the ever changing needs of our students worldwide, and help them reach out to the world through Online English language learning. Our pool of professional educators will definitely be able to fit our students’ schedule requirements.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div id="menu2" class="tab-pane fade">
                    <div class="tittle">
                      <h3 class="text-left">Academic Alliance</h3>
                      <p class="text-left"><i>Comprised of a group of educators, university administrators, and consultants, English Online Study assists students and academic institutions in meeting their educational goals efficiently and affordably.</i> </p>
                      <hr>
                    </div>
                    <p>In formulating our study pathway programs, we mediate with our university partners and alliances to create optimal delivery models that address the specific educational needs of the student and their home institutions.</p>
                    <p>Offered in different parts of the world and spanning across various academic disciplines and levels, EOS´s pathway programs and services provide students with the competencies, skills and readiness for their desire degree program.<br>
                    Through the Academic Alliance for English we conduct research and help innovate, supporting both internal and external projects with material or human aid.</p>
                    <p>Researchers, linguists and technical experts are encouraged and backed to pursue, initiate, develop, complete or disseminate their academic projects in the fields of English learning in particular, or e-learning in general.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div id="menu3" class="tab-pane fade">
                    <div class="tittle text-left">
                      <h3 class="text-left">Social Responsibility</h3>
                      <p class="text-left"><i>In this present era of Globalization as corporations are becoming more aware of their social responsibilities the traditional responses of companies contributing to good causes are dramatically changing from mere philanthropy. Despite the worthwhile support given by many corporations, an enormous amount could still be done. Globalization could lead to benchmarks, better jobs, higher standards of living, but could result in the gap between developed and developing countries particularly due to language barriers & access to Global language i.e. English.</i> </p>
                      <p class="text-left"><i>In EOS we are driven by the ambitious dream of helping to spread English learning to everyone in the world. This includes addressing the educational needs of youths and adults regardless of their cultural background and socioeconomic status.</i> </p>
                      <hr>
                    </div>
                    <h6>Inspiring Learning and Knowledge</h6>
                    <p>The purpose of English Online Study platform is to help people achieve their life goals. Thousands of education institutions, employers, professional bodies around the world recognize English Online Study, and there is a constant effort to ensure they are accepted as widely as possible.</p>
                    <h6>Assisting Professionals</h6>
                    <p>Teachers are valuable to us and we support them in numerous ways. We also provide extensive advice and support for teachers through Teaching English and English Online Study Teacher.<br>
                    English Online Study has an equal opportunities policy in place to enable all of its employees around the world to enjoy opportunities in the workplace regardless of gender, ethnic origin, age, disability or religion.</p>
                    <h6>Environmental Influence</h6>
                    <p>A growing number of environmentally friendly initiatives have been incorporated into our everyday operations to reduce any damage to the environment. Recent moves to minimize our carbon footprint have included offering computer-based versions of learning materials, introducing paperless administration systems, and moving towards a waste re-cycling system for our EOS headquarters thereby doing a little contribution to save our beautiful Earth.</p>
                  </div>
